flavor_text_entries.alpha-sapphire:
It drifts in warm seas. It always returns to where it
was born, no matter how far it may have drifted.
flavor_text_entries.diamond:
A Pokémon that lives in warm seas.
It inflates the flotation sac on its
head to drift and search for food.

flavor_text_entries.legends-arceus:
Can be seen floating offshore during seasons when the seas are
warm. Its azure body blends in with the ocean waters—logic
suggests this is a defense mechanism against natural predators.
